steps.instruction: Enter the roundabout and take the 2nd exit
Enter the roundabout and take the 2nd exit onto Şile Otoyolu, D-020
Keep right onto Reşadiye Kavşağı, O-7
Keep left onto Çamlık Kavşağı, O-7
Keep right onto Yavuz Selim Caddesi
Continue straight onto Namık Kemal Caddesi
Arrive at 33. Sokak, on the right
